{"name": "mintrans", "metadata": {"name": "mintrans", "version": "1.1.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/DedInc/mintrans", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests", "aiohttp", "asyncio"], "summary": "Mintrans is a free API wrapper that utilizes Bing, DeepL, and Google Translate for translation purposes.", "upload_time": 1734060041}, "documentation": ["# \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f mintrans - A translation API wrapper \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f\r\n\r\nmintrans is a free API wrapper that utilizes Bing, DeepL, and Google Translate for translation purposes. \ud83e\udd16\r\n\r\n## \ud83d\udca1 How to use \ud83d\udca1\r\n\r\n```python \r\nfrom mintrans import BingTranslator, DeepLTranslator, GoogleTranslator\r\nfrom mintrans import RateLimitException\r\n\r\ntext = 'Hello World!'\r\nfrom_lang = 'en'  \r\nto_lang = 'fr'\r\n\r\n# Bing Translator\r\nbing_translator = BingTranslator()  \r\nbing_translation = bing_translator.translate(text, from_lang, to_lang)\r\nprint(bing_translation)\r\n\r\n# DeepL Translator  \r\ndeepl_translator = DeepLTranslator()\r\ntry:\r\n\tdeepl_translation = deepl_translator.translate(text, from_lang, to_lang)\r\n\tprint(deepl_translation)\r\nexcept RateLimitException:\r\n\tprint('Limit of DeepL Translator reached!')\r\n\r\n# Google Translator\r\ngoogle_translator = GoogleTranslator()  \r\ngoogle_translation = google_translator.translate(text, from_lang, to_lang)\r\nprint(google_translation)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## \ud83d\udd11 Features \ud83d\udd11\r\n\r\n- Bing, DeepL and Google translators for more translation options!\r\n- Easy switching between translators.\r\n- Supports 100+ languages across translators. \ud83c\udf0d\r\n\r\n## \ud83c\udfc6 Examples \ud83c\udfc6\r\n\r\n```python\r\ntext = 'This is a longer text to test the translation.'\r\n\r\nbing_translation = bing_translator.translate(text, 'en', 'es') \r\n\r\ndeepl_translation = deepl_translator.translate(text, 'en', 'de')\r\n\r\ngoogle_translation = google_translator.translate(text, 'en', 'fr')  \r\n```\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "mintrans", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "mintrans.AsyncBingTranslator", "xref": {"fqname": "mintrans.async_mintrans.AsyncBingTranslator", "project": null}}, {"name": "mintrans.AsyncDeepLTranslator", "xref": {"fqname": "mintrans.async_mintrans.AsyncDeepLTranslator", "project": null}}, {"name": "mintrans.AsyncGoogleTranslator", "xref": {"fqname": "mintrans.async_mintrans.AsyncGoogleTranslator", "project": null}}, {"name": "mintrans.BingTranslator", "xref": {"fqname": "mintrans.BingTranslator", "project": null}}, {"name": "mintrans.DeepLTranslator", "xref": {"fqname": "mintrans.DeepLTranslator", "project": null}}, {"name": "mintrans.get_random_user_agent_async", "xref": {"fqname": "mintrans.async_mintrans.get_random_user_agent_async", "project": null}}, {"name": "mintrans.GoogleTranslator", "xref": {"fqname": "mintrans.GoogleTranslator", "project": null}}, {"name": "mintrans.RateLimitException", "xref": {"fqname": "mintrans.RateLimitException", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "mintrans.async_mintrans", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "mintrans.async_mintrans.get_random_user_agent_async", "asynchronous": true, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mintrans.async_mintrans.async_retry_on_rate_limit", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "max_attempts", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "delay", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "mintrans.async_mintrans.AsyncBingTranslator", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "mintrans.async_mintrans.AsyncBingTranslator.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mintrans.